    <string name="step_one_description">Lumen is a daily check-in that helps you understand your emotional patterns over time &#8212; gently, and at your own pace. No account is required, but you can create one later
    to enable device syncing if you\'d like.</string>
    <string name="step_two_description">Your name is how Lumen will greet you each day.</string>
    <string name="step_four_description">Choose as many as feel right.</string>
    <string name="step_five_description">One check-in per day. A single, intentional moment. You can always this time from the Profile screen.</string>
    <string name="step_seven_description">It only takes a couple of minutes and will give you a meaningful starting point.</string>

